cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.RO 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the task of dynamic hand gesture recognition using 3D-CNNs. The paper also proposes a novel framework for leveraging the knowledge from multiple modalities, which falls under the sub-category of Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the use of multimodal data, which could be categorized under Multimedia (cs.MM). The task of hand gesture recognition also has applications in Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) and Robotics (cs.RO), making these sub-categories likely as well.
